works.description: While the entrepreneurs are getting more creative in designing their business cards to give more visibility to their creative businesses, there are other ways to get the eyeballs and show off your riches when you are super-rich. While the gold business cards we have earlier told you about would just appeal to the oil-rich sheikhs or those with blingy tastes, the real carbon fiber card by Carbon Fiber Designs is perfect for everyone; from geeks to the business tycoons, known for their love for autos.
